{"tid":1669890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：不要高調支持加泰，顧掂自己先。","createTime":"2019-10-22T22:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T06:12:10.000Z","uid":86509,"like":350,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"7730869559bac1bbc570d614d867b1b91e65e335","tid":1669890,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:35:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157517044102225/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10157517044102225%2F&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=d7c84805\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157517044102225/</a><br />\n陳雲：不要玩膠，顧掂自己先。香港有示威者申請舉辦集會聲援加他隆尼亞的獨立分離運動。看來衙門會批准囉，因為是陷害香港用的。<br />\n共和黨海外發言人Solomon Yue出推特帖文提醒香港人，加泰的人支持香港是可以的，但香港高調支持加泰，是令中共可以聲稱有證據顯示香港人從事分裂運動，令美國參議院未必通過香港人權法案。<br />\n（不過，Solomon Yue 也誤解了「時代革命」，那是港獨的主張，並非自治）"},{"pid":"65326b49d6620badc26acf775b970dfcb30c5865","tid":1669890,"uid":134071,"like":61,"dislike":12,"score":49,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:36:41.000Z","msg":"今次大部分認同陳雲<br />\n<br />\n但佢點都要去抹黑時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bfb859d1572ff5e7ff34d3b30de7dfc1745a0e5","tid":1669890,"uid":70487,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:36:44.000Z","msg":"加泰係搞緊獨立，<br />\n<br />\n香港憑咩去支援人地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d7ae391de7129be6780da46ea2c92b283ba53b","tid":1669890,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:37:18.000Z","msg":"借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[晨早流流]三分鐘Twitter 戰線傳送門 10月23號<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1669882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1669882</a>"},{"pid":"df4d575bfcb16c940f467e892ced15cc72c750b6","tid":1669890,"uid":188176,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"65326b49d6620badc26acf775b970dfcb30c5865",